// SOURCE: The Ruby JavaScript (RJS) to destroy a following relationship.
// update the follow form with the unfollow partial (which is what should show after a successful following) and update the follower count.
// This uses the 'escape_javascript' function, which is needed to escape out the result when inserting HTML in a JavaScript file.

$("#follow_form").html("<%= escape_javascript(render('users/follow')) %>")
$("#followers").html('<%= @user.followers.count %>')